title: Are You Interested in Transferring to UCLA? Come Talk with the UCLA Peer Mentor on ...
text: ( Source : Los Angeles Valley College ) The UCLA Peer Mentor will be on-campus to answer questions about transferring to UCLA on October 19 from 10 a.m.-2 p.m. at the Career / Transfer Center . Student can also schedule a one-on-one appointment
